snippet.title: LONDON FIELDS MOVIE TRAILER OFFICIAL 2018 Amber Heard Thriller Mystery Movie YouTube
snippet.description:
In the movie London Fields, (which is based on the NY Times best selling novel of the same name by Martin Amis), clairvoyant femme fatale, Nicola Six (Amber Heard), has been living with a dark premonition of her impending death by murder.

She begins a tangled love affair with three uniquely different men: one of whom she knows will be her murderer.

Cara Delevingne, Jason Isaacs, Billy Bob Thornton, Theo James, Jim Sturgess and Jaimie Alexander co-star in the movie London Fields.

Director of the film, Martin Cullen, has only worked behind the camera on music videos. This is his first movie. He may be best known for directing the Adele music video, Chasing Pavements and the Katy Perry music video California Gurls.
